headline: 3 Retail Stocks That May Gain From Trump's 2026 Tax Refunds
summary: Larger 2026 tax refunds and stimulus from President Donald Trump's tax changes could drive a spending boost for value retailers. Bank of America highlights Burlington, Ollie's and Ross as potential beneficiaries.
